Vol / Page: 3
Edition:
Quote: Squatting will now become the order of things in New Zealand, as well as in New South Wales; but with this difference in favour of this country, that the squatter requires no license in this country; that his sheep and cattle are always secure under the protection of the natives, with his own superintendance [sic].
